title: AVP-Tales From the 201
description:
AVP 

Tales From the 201 (2016)

Description: AVP is an up-and-coming rap group focused around a lyrical style of rap. Tales From the 201 is their debut album. AVP's main influences are the Wu-Tang Clan, Redman, Busta Rhymes, MF Doom, and Eminem.
